===Spookality 2024 pins===
[[File:VRChat-Spookality-Pin-Set-P-2 1000x.png.webp|thumb|VRChat's Spookality 2024 pin set]]
A glow-in-the-dark [[Special:MyLanguage/Spookality 2024|Spookality 2024]] themed enamel pin set was released, featuring [[Special:MyLanguage/VRCat|VRCat]], and a VRChat logo. These pins were available in October 2024. The campaign ran from October 1 to October 30, 2024.